perdersi Stefi Talman. Il negozio si trova in posizione ottimale, nella Oberdorfstrasse, nel centro storico a destra della Limmat, tra la chiesa di Grossmünster e la fermata del tram Bellevue.</p>','Stefi Talman','Stefi Talman','Stefi Talman','Stefi Talman','Innovatives Zürcher Design finden Liebhaberinnen und Liebhaber bei Stefi Talman.','Shoe enthusiasts can find innovative Zurich designs at Stefi Talman’s store.','Chez Stefi Talman, les amoureux du design innovant zurichois trouveront leur bonheur.','Da Stefi Talman si trova innovativo design zurighese.','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/web_zuerich_shopping_stefi_talman_1280x960_26760.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/web_zuerich_shopping_stefi_talman_1280x960_26768.jpg',NULL,955271639,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
