ecken.','Explore the city in a relaxed manner and discover unfamiliar places quickly and easily.','Traversez la ville à vélo électrique pour sortir des sentiers battus. ','Esplorare la città a bordo di una comoda e-bike e scoprire nuovi angoli.','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/web_zuerich_ebike_tour_miete_1280x960.jpg','2019-10-11 10:58:20 +0200','Vermietung exklusiv durch Zürich Tourismus','Exclusive rental through Zurich Tourism','Vélos électriques élégant et de qualité',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
