ti trovano moda e calzature, ma anche accessori e gadget di lifestyle. Cordiale e preparato, il personale conosce la storia dietro ogni prodotto e aiuta volentieri i visitatori.</p><p>Altra filiale:</p><ul><li>Sihlcity, Kanderplatz 1</li></ul>','Circle – The Sustainable Shop','Circle – The Sustainable Shop','Circle – The Sustainable Shop','Circle – The Sustainable Shop','Der Eco Concept Store im Herzen der Altstadt mit nachhaltig und fairen Produkten von Mode über Schuhe bis hin zu Accessoires.','The eco concept store in the heart of the Old Town, selling sustainably and ethically produced products, such as fashion, shoes, and accessories.','Ce magasin écologique au cœur de la vieille ville propose des produits durables et équitables comme les vêtements, les accessoires et les chaussures.','L’Eco Concept Store nel centro storico propone moda, calzature e accessori sostenibili ed equosolidali.','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/web_zuerich_thecircle-sustainable_shop_1280x960_24990.jpg','2020-01-27 08:02:46 +0100','Kompetente, freundliche Beratung','Competent, friendly service ','Conseils amicaux et compétents','Consulenza competente e cordiale','CH','Zürich',8001,'Brunngasse 3','+41 43 243 69 21','kundendienst@circleshop.net','www.circleshop.ch',47.373236900000,8.544154700000,'POINT (47.3732369 8.5441547)',1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Montag bis Mittwoch, 10.30 &ndash; 18.30 Uhr<br />Donnerstag 10.30 &ndash; 19.30 Uhr<br />Freitag 10.30 &ndash; 18.30 Uhr<br />Samstag 10.30 &ndash; 17.30 Uhr</p>','<p>Monday &ndash; Wednesday, 10.30am &ndash; 6.30pm<br />Thursday, 10.30am &ndash; 7.30pm<br />Friday, 10.30am &ndash; 6.30pm<br />Saturday, 10.30am &ndash; 5.30pm</p>','<p>Du lundi au mercredi, 10h30 &ndash; 18h30<br />Jeudi, 10h30 &ndash; 19h30<br />Vendredi, 10h30 &ndash; 18h30<br />Samedi, 10h30 &ndash; 17h30</p>','<p>Da lunedì a mercoledì 10.30 &ndash; 18.30<br />Giovedì 10.30 &ndash; 19.30<br />Venerdì 10.30 &ndash; 18.30<br />Sabato 10.30 &ndash; 17.30</p>','M