 à la « Marktlücke ».','Al Marktlücke si trovano pezzi unici realizzati a mano, trouvailles e accessori di vario genere.','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/web_zurich_shopping_marktluecke_02.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Einzigartige Accessoires, schöne Dinge und Trouvaillen','Unique items, beautiful accessories and treasures ','Accessoires uniques, superbes objets et raretés','Accessori favolosi, cose belle e trouvailles',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/imagegallery/web_zurich_shopping_marktluecke_03.jpg',NULL,NULL,'Mitten in der Zürcher Altstadt','In the heart of Zurich’s Old Town ','Au centre de la vieille ville de Zurich','Nel cuore del centro storico zurighese',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
