    (2480,'https://schema.org/','Place','Zurich Tourism www.zuerich.com','Zürich Tourismus www.zuerich.com','Zürich Tourismo www.zuerich.com','Zürich Tourisme www.zuerich.com','BY-SA','Food & Delicacy','Jelmoli','Jelmoli','Jelmoli','Jelmoli',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Jelmoli - The House of Brands ist in 5 Minuten zu Fuss vom Hauptbahnhof an der Zürcher Bahnhofstrasse zu erreichen. Der grösste Premium Department Store der Stadt Zürich wurde nach Vorbildern aus Paris und London 1899 erstellt und gehört heute zu den besten Adressen Zürichs. Exklusiv für jeden Lifestyle und jede Generation finden sich Topmarken für Damen, Herren und Kinder. Neben der renommierten Parfümerie gibt es ein breites Angebot an Mode, Accessoires, Schuhen, Sport und Living.</p><p>Im Untergeschoss befindet sich der Jelmoli &laquo;Food Market&raquo; mit zahlreichen Highlights wie dem schweizweit ersten Käse-Humidor, &nbsp;einer erlesenen Food- und Weinauswahl und einem exklusiven Gastronomie-Angebot.</p><p>Diese Filiale bietet übrigens &laquo;Personal Shopping&raquo; in folgenden Sprachen an: Deutsch, Englisch, Französisch.</p>','<p>Jelmoli &ndash; The House of Brands is situated on Bahnhofstrasse, a five-minute walk from the Zurich main station. Zurich&rsquo;s largest premium department store, it was designed in 1899 based on Paris and London models and ranks among the city&rsquo;s most sophisticated fashion houses. A range of top-quality brands for men, women and children provides something for every lifestyle and generation. In addition to the renowned perfumery, you can find a wide selection of fashion items, accessories, shoes, sport articles and home products.</p><p>The well-known Food Market is located below ground level and offers several highlights including Switzerland&#39;s first cheese humidor, a select range of food and wines, as well as an exclusive choice of restaurants.</p><p>Incidentally, this branch offers a personal shopping service in the following languages: German, English, French.</p>','<p>Jelmoli - The House of Brands, à 5 minutes à pied de la Gare Centrale, est le plus grand centre commercial shop in shop de Suisse. Fondé en 1899 sur les modèles parisiens et londoniens, le grand magasin compte aujourd&rsquo;hui parmi les meilleures adresses de Zürich. Au sous-sol, Jelmoli propose un grand choix de produits alimentaires et gastronomiques (Food Market). La plupart des produits peuvent également être dégustés à l&rsquo;un des nombreux petits bars.</p><p>Cette succursale propose du &laquo;&nbsp;shopping personnalisé&nbsp;&raquo; dans les langues suivantes&nbsp;: allemand, anglais et français.</p>','<p>Jelmoli - The House of Brands. Raggiungibile in 5 minuti a piedi dalla Stazione Centrale, è il grande magazzino shop-in-shop più grande della Svizzera. Costruito nel 1899 sui modelli di Parigi e Londra, Jelmoli rappresenta oggi uno dei migliori indirizzi di Zurigo. Alimenti e specialità gastronomiche si trovano nel seminterrato (Food Market). La maggior parte dei prodotti può essere degustata in uno dei numerosi barettini.</p><p>Questa filiale propone anche il servizio &quot;Personal Shopping&quot; nelle seguenti lingue: tedesco, inglese, francese.</p>',NULL,'Jelmoli',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/web_zurich_shopping_jelmoli_01.jpg','2020-03-04 16:53:18 +0100',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'CH','Zürich',8001,'Seidengasse 1','+41 44 220 44 11','info@jelmoli.ch','http://www.jelmoli.ch',47.374243300000,8.537660700000,'POINT (47.3742433 8.5376607)',1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Montag &ndash; Freitag 09.30 &ndash; 20.00 Uhr<br>Samstag 9.00 &ndash; 20.00 Uhr</p>','<p>Monday to Friday 9.30am &ndash; 8.00pm<br>Saturday 9.00am &ndash; 8.00pm</p>','<p>Du lundi au vendredi 9h30 &ndash; 20h<br>Samedi 9h &ndash; 20h</p>','<p>Da lunedì a venerdì 9.30 &ndash; 20.00<br>SAbato 9.00 &ndash; 20.00</p>','Monday,Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday',NULL,'Indoors',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,N