    (2036,'https://schema.org/','Place','Zurich Tourism www.zuerich.com','Zürich Tourismus www.zuerich.com','Zürich Tourismo www.zuerich.com','Zürich Tourisme www.zuerich.com','BY-SA','Souvenirs & Gifts','Changemaker','Changemaker',NULL,'Changemaker',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Das Angebot ist breit: Von T-Shirts bis hin zu edlen Wollschals und Keramikvasen. Jedes Produkt hat seine eigene Geschichte. Sie beginnt bei Designern mit einer Passion für das Sinnvolle. Sie handelt von fair entlöhnten Arbeitern und von Kleinmanufakturen, die ihre Verantwortung gegenüber Umwelt und Natur ernst nehmen. Damit man weiss, was man kauft.</p>','<p>The range is wide &ndash; from T-shirts to fine woolen scarves, and ceramic vases. Each product has its own story. It begins with designers with a passion for functional design. It is about fair pay for workers and small manufacturing outlets which take their responsibilities towards the environment and the countryside seriously. So you know what you&rsquo;re buying.</p>',NULL,'<p>L&rsquo;offerta è davvero ampia: da T-shirt a eleganti sciarpe di lana e vasi di ceramica. Ogni prodotto ha una storia a sé, che inizia da designer con una passione per le cose intelligenti. Una passione che coinvolge lavoratori e piccole manifatture retribuiti onestamente, che prendono sul serio la propria responsabilità nei confronti dell&rsquo;ambiente e della natura. Per sapere esattamente cosa si acquista.</p>','Changemaker','Changemaker',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/zurich_shopping_platzhalter_urban_05.jpg','2018-10-16 10:29:01 +0200',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'CH','Zürich',8001,'Marktgasse 10','+41 44 251 21 20','zuerich@changemaker.ch','www.changemaker.ch',47.371794500000,8.543542200000,'POINT (47.3717945 8.543542199999999)',1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Montag – Freitag 10.00 – 19.00 Uhr<br>Samstag 10.00 – 17.00 Uhr</p>','<p>Monday to Friday 10.00am – 7.00pm <br>Saturday 10am – 5pm</p>','<p>Du lundi au vendredi