egato assortimento della casa, sono soprattutto le diverse &ldquo;Heisse Schoggi&rdquo; (cioccolate calde) a entusiasmare i clienti.</p>','Schwarzenbach','Schwarzenbach','Schwarzenbach','Schwarzenbach','Das Spezialitätengeschäft im Herzen der Zürcher Altstadt begeistert Kunden aus aller Welt.','The specialty store in the heart of Zurich’s Old Town delights customers from all over the world.','Cette épicerie au cœur de la vieille ville zurichoise séduit les clients du monde entier. ','Il negozio coloniale nel cuore del centro storico zurighese entusiasma clienti di tutto il mondo.','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/zurich_shopping_07.jpg','2020-01-21 10:18:47 +0100','Shop mit angrenzendem Café','With adjacent café','Magasin avec café attenant','Negozio con caffè annesso','CH','Zürich',8001,'Münstergasse 19',' +41 44 261 13 15','info@schwarzenbach.ch','www.schwarzenbach.ch',47.371413200000,8.543905100000,'POINT (47.3714132 8.5439051)',1,NULL,'Shopping in Zurich, Niederdorf: Schwarzenbach Kolonialwaren Groceries','Shopping à Zurich, Niederdorf: Epicerie Schwarzenbach Kolonialwaren ','Shopping a Zurigo, Niederdorf: Schwarzenbach Kolonialwaren','<p>Montag bis Freitag, 09.00 &ndash; 18.30 Uhr<br />Samstag, 09.00 &ndash; 17.00 Uhr</p>','<p>Monday to Friday 9.00am &ndash; 6.30pm<br>Saturday 9.00am &ndash; 5.00pm</p>','<p>Du lundi au vendredi, 9h &ndash; 18h30<br />Samedi, 9h &ndash; 17h</p>','<p>Da lunedì a venerdì, 9.00 &ndash; 18.30<br />Sabato, 9.00 &ndash; 17.00&nbsp;</p>','Monday,Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
